stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> planned : run_terraform_plan_mcp called\n(execution_id created)

    planned --> approval_pending : plan summary shown to user\n(Approve / Reject buttons rendered)

    approval_pending --> approved : user clicks Approve
    approval_pending --> rejected : user clicks Reject

    rejected --> resolved : admin marks resolved

    approved --> applying : run_terraform_apply_mcp called

    applying --> applied : terraform apply succeeds
    applying --> failed : terraform apply fails

    applied --> rollback : user triggers destroy\n(run_terraform_destroy_mcp)
    applied --> resolved : admin marks resolved\n(mark_execution_resolved)

    rollback --> resolved : terraform destroy completes

    failed --> resolved : admin marks resolved

    resolved --> [*]
